title: Cal Smart Chipotle-Honey Beef Bowls with Green Onion Rice
description: This hearty beef bowl is full of wholesome goodness! We even snuck some spinach into the beef mix for an added veggie boost. Pickled radishes and a sweet and spicy chipotle-honey sauce brighten each bite.

